To use Grid Submission, Copy this directory to the run directory,
then edit 01SubmitToGrid_Simple.py to include your grid nickname,
config file, etc...

To setup a production role, run the following lines:
setupATLAS
export RUCIO_ACCOUNT=phys-higgs
lsetup rucio panda pyami
voms-proxy-init -voms atlas:/atlas/phys-higgs/Role=production
